  ('Seated Isometric Calf Hold (Soleus)', 'seated-isometric-calf-hold-soleus', 'isometrics', NULL, 'Hold a mid-range plantarflexed position under load. Some athletes get analgesia, some don''t (Achilles replication failed) — we track your response, we don''t promise relief.', 'Hold a mid-range plantarflexed position under load. Some athletes get analgesia, some don''t (Achilles replication failed) — we track your response, we don''t promise relief.', ARRAY['Hold steady, don''t bounce','Breathe through the hold','Log whether it eased the pain — we track it per athlete'], ARRAY['calves'], ARRAY['soleus'], 'Isometric Plantarflexion', '{}', FALSE, 8, 4, NULL, 30, NULL, 'beginner', '{}', TRUE, ARRAY['soleus','achilles'], 'isometric', 'knee_bent', 'none', 2, 'CONTESTED', 1),
